flowchart LR
  user[Operator]
  openclaw[OpenClaw Gateway<br/>agent + dashboard]
  skill[mautic-control skill<br/>procedures + examples]
  plugin[OpenClaw Mautic plugin<br/>typed tools]
  client[Mautic API client<br/>auth + request wrapper]
  api[Mautic REST API<br/>/api and /api/v2]
  hooks[Mautic webhooks<br/>/api/hooks + event triggers]
  cli[Mautic console<br/>cron, imports, cache, plugins]
  db[(MariaDB)]
  workspace[(Shared workspace<br/>files, skills, mautic)]

  user -->|natural language| openclaw
  openclaw -->|loads guidance| skill
  openclaw -->|calls tools| plugin
  plugin -->|read/write entities| client
  client -->|contacts, segments, campaigns,<br/>emails, forms, assets, reports| api
  client -->|create and manage outbound events| hooks
  plugin -->|maintenance and bulk jobs| cli
  api --> db
  hooks --> db
  cli --> db
  plugin -->|import/export staging| workspace
  openclaw --> workspace

  subgraph Control["Control coverage"]
    c1[CRUD any API resource]
    c2[Bulk import/export]
    c3[Campaign and segment operations]
    c4[Webhook event wiring]
    c5[Health checks and audits]
  end

  plugin --> c1
  plugin --> c2
  plugin --> c3
  plugin --> c4
  plugin --> c5
